AssetBuilder
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     Asset asset = Asset.builder()
             .key("{key}")
             .plusSources(sourcesBuilder -> sourcesBuilder)
             .name(nameBuilder -> nameBuilder)
             .build()
